item.title: Resume and FAQ
item.description: FAQ you may have. Q: Where are you now? A: I am currently in Portland Oregon but will be moving to Milwaukkee Wisconsin Dec 10 , I spent the last year in Hua Hin Thailand. Q: Are you willing to relocate? A: Yes I am willing to relocate for the right job. Q: What kind of job are you looking for? A:Looking for full time job that is stable and has good career advancement obituaries.
